<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-4919] StorageProxy.getRangeSlice sometimes returns incorrect number of columns</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-4919</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When deployed on a single node, number of columns is correct.&lt;br/&gt;
When deployed on a cluster, total number of returned columns is slightly lower than desired. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
